        protected void extractBeanValues(Object source,
                                 String[] nameMapping)
                          throws org.supercsv.exception.SuperCsvReflectionException
        Extracts the bean values, using the supplied name mapping array.
        パラメータ:
        source - the bean
        nameMapping - the name mapping
        例外:
        NullPointerException - if source or nameMapping are null
        org.supercsv.exception.SuperCsvReflectionException - if there was a reflection exception extracting the bean value
